snippet.title: Shin'en: FAST Racing League (WiiWare) Trailer
snippet.description:
http://fast.shinen.com/
Switch the phase - Win the Race
In the year 2112 the masses are fascinated by extreme high speed races. The latest antigrav racing technology introduced phase shifting. Perfect phase matching of track and racing machine is the key to stay alive. 
Warm up your engines, the future is now...

To get the full super-smooth 60 frames per second experience, grab our high-quality video at http://fast.shinen.com/videos.php (download link below the embedded video)
